pycurator.collectors.type_collectors.OpenMLCollector

pycurator.collectors.type_collectors.OpenMLCollector#

class pycurator.collectors.type_collectors.OpenMLCollector(search_types: Optional[collections.abc.Collection[pycurator._typing.SearchType]] = None, credentials: Optional[str] = None)[source]#

OpenML collector for search type queries.

Parameters

  • search_types (list-like, optional) – Types to search over. Can be (re)set via set_search_types() or passed in directly to search functions.

  • credentials (str, optional (default=None)) – OpenML API key.
